{
  "chapter": 6,
  "chapter_summary": "决斗前夕，杜雷与同伙拇指、孔雀研究傅红雪的资料，杜雷指出傅红雪患有羊癫疯的致命弱点。傅红雪在倪家废园等待杜雷，遇到自称倪家二小姐的倪慧，她试图接近傅红雪却以暗杀告终。杜雷故意让傅红雪久等以消耗其意志，而拇指和孔雀则趁机准备刺杀中毒的燕南飞。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "拇指",
      "listener": "char_du_lei",
      "text": "你看过了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_lei",
      "speaker_name": "杜雷",
      "listener": "char_mu_zhi",
      "text": "嗯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "拇指",
      "listener": "char_du_lei",
      "text": "我也知道你决不会满意的，但是这已经是我们所能弄到手的全部资料。对傅红雪这个人，谁也不会知道得更多！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_lei",
      "speaker_name": "杜雷",
      "listener": "char_mu_zhi",
      "text": "很好。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "拇指",
      "listener": "char_du_lei",
      "text": "这些资料对你有没有用？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_lei",
      "speaker_name": "杜雷",
      "listener": "char_mu_zhi",
      "text": "没有。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "拇指",
      "listener": "char_du_lei",
      "text": "一点用都没有？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_lei",
      "speaker_name": "杜雷",
      "listener": "char_mu_zhi",
      "text": "你的资料中遗漏了两点，是最重要两点！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "拇指",
      "listener": "char_du_lei",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_lei",
      "speaker_name": "杜雷",
      "listener": "char_mu_zhi",
      "text": "他以前曾经被一个女人骗过，骗得很惨。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "拇指",
      "listener": "char_du_lei",
      "text": "这女人是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_lei",
      "speaker_name": "杜雷",
      "listener": "char_mu_zhi",
      "text": "是个叫翠浓的婊子。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "拇指",
      "listener": "char_du_lei",
      "text": "我总觉得奇怪，为什么越聪明的男人，越容易上婊子的当？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kong_que",
      "speaker_name": "孔雀",
      "listener": "char_mu_zhi",
      "text": "因为聪明的男人只喜欢聪明的女人，聪明的女人却通常都是婊子。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "拇指",
      "listener": "char_kong_que",
      "text": "我知道你恨女人，却想不到你恨得这么厉害。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_lei",
      "speaker_name": "杜雷",
      "listener": "char_kong_que",
      "text": "看来他一定也上过女人的当。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kong_que",
      "speaker_name": "孔雀",
      "listener": "char_du_lei",
      "text": "你说的第二点是什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_lei",
      "speaker_name": "杜雷",
      "listener": "char_kong_que",
      "text": "他有病。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "拇指",
      "listener": "char_du_lei",
      "text": "什么病？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_lei",
      "speaker_name": "杜雷",
      "listener": "char_mu_zhi",
      "text": "羊癫疯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "拇指",
      "listener": "char_du_lei",
      "text": "他的病发作时，是不是也像别人一样，会口吐白沫，倒在地上打滚？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_lei",
      "speaker_name": "杜雷",
      "listener": "char_mu_zhi",
      "text": "羊癫疯只有一种！",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "拇指",
      "listener": "char_du_lei",
      "text": "一个有羊癫疯的跛子，居然能练成天下无双的快刀。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_lei",
      "speaker_name": "杜雷",
      "listener": "char_mu_zhi",
      "text": "他下过苦功。据说他每天至少要花四个时辰练刀。从四五岁的时候开始，每天就至少要拔刀一万两千次。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "拇指",
      "listener": "char_du_lei",
      "text": "想不到你对他这个人知道得比我们还多。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_lei",
      "speaker_name": "杜雷",
      "listener": "char_mu_zhi",
      "text": "江湖名人榜上的每个人我都知道得很清楚，因为我已花了整整五个月的功夫，去收集他们的资料，又花了五个月的功夫去研究。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "拇指",
      "listener": "char_du_lei",
      "text": "你用在傅红雪身上的功夫一定比研究别人都多。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "拇指",
      "listener": "char_du_lei",
      "text": "你研究出了什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_lei",
      "speaker_name": "杜雷",
      "listener": "char_mu_zhi",
      "text": "他一向刀不离手，只因为他一直用的都是这把刀，至少已用了二十年。现在这把刀几乎已成了他身体的一部分，他使用这把刀，几乎比别人使用自己的手指还要灵活如意。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "拇指",
      "listener": "char_du_lei",
      "text": "但我却知道，他用的那把刀并不十分好。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_lei",
      "speaker_name": "杜雷",
      "listener": "char_mu_zhi",
      "text": "能杀人的刀，就是好刀！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kong_que",
      "speaker_name": "孔雀",
      "listener": "char_du_lei",
      "text": "如果我们能拿到他的刀……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_lei",
      "speaker_name": "杜雷",
      "listener": "char_kong_que",
      "text": "没有人能拿到他的刀。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kong_que",
      "speaker_name": "孔雀",
      "listener": "char_du_lei",
      "text": "每件事都有例外的。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_lei",
      "speaker_name": "杜雷",
      "listener": "char_kong_que",
      "text": "这件事没有例外。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kong_que",
      "speaker_name": "孔雀",
      "listener": "char_du_lei",
      "text": "他的病通常都在什么时候发作？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_lei",
      "speaker_name": "杜雷",
      "listener": "char_kong_que",
      "text": "每当他的愤怒和悲哀到了不可忍受时，他的病就会发作。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kong_que",
      "speaker_name": "孔雀",
      "listener": "char_du_lei",
      "text": "如果你能在他病发时出手……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_lei",
      "speaker_name": "杜雷",
      "listener": "char_kong_que",
      "text": "你以为我是什么人？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kong_que",
      "speaker_name": "孔雀",
      "listener": "char_du_lei",
      "text": "我也知道你不肯做这种事的，但我们却不妨叫别人去做。如果我们能找个人先去气气他，让他……",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_lei",
      "speaker_name": "杜雷",
      "listener": "char_kong_que",
      "text": "我只希望你们明白一件事。这是我与他两个人之间的决斗，无论谁胜谁负，都和别人全无关系。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "拇指",
      "listener": "char_du_lei",
      "text": "和公子也全无关系？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "拇指",
      "listener": "char_du_lei",
      "text": "如果你还没有忘记公子，就至少应做到一件事。让他等，多等些时候，等到他心烦意乱时你再去。这一战你是胜是负，是活是死，我们都不关心，可是我们也不想替你去收尸。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_lei",
      "speaker_name": "杜雷",
      "listener": "char_mu_zhi",
      "text": "什么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ni_hui",
      "speaker_name": "倪慧",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "你不问我为什么笑？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ni_hui",
      "speaker_name": "倪慧",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "我在笑你。你站在那里的样子，看起来就像个呆子。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ni_hui",
      "speaker_name": "倪慧",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "你也不问我是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_ni_hui",
      "text": "你是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ni_hui",
      "speaker_name": "倪慧",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "我就在等着你问我这句话。你知不知道你现在站着的这块地，是谁家的地？你凭什么大摇大摆地在这块地上走来走去？",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ni_hui",
      "speaker_name": "倪慧",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "这地方是倪家的。我就是倪家的二小姐，只要我高兴，我随时都可以赶你出去。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ni_hui",
      "speaker_name": "倪慧",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "可是我当然不会赶你出去的，因为……因为我喜欢你。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ni_hui",
      "speaker_name": "倪慧",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "我说我喜欢你，其实是假的。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_ni_hui",
      "text": "你知道我？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ni_hui",
      "speaker_name": "倪慧",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "当然知道！",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_ni_hui",
      "text": "知道些什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ni_hui",
      "speaker_name": "倪慧",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "我不但知道你的武功，连你姓什么，叫什么，我都知道！",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ni_hui",
      "speaker_name": "倪慧",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "别人都说你是个怪物，可是我倒觉得你非但不怪，而且长得还蛮好看的。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_ni_hui",
      "text": "这地方只剩下你一个人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ni_hui",
      "speaker_name": "倪慧",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "一个人又怎么样？难道你还敢欺负我？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_ni_hui",
      "text": "平时你也不在这里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ni_hui",
      "speaker_name": "倪慧",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "我为什么要一个人呆在这种鬼地方？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_ni_hui",
      "text": "现在你为什么还不走？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ni_hui",
      "speaker_name": "倪慧",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "这是我的家，我要来就来，要走就走，为什么要受别人指挥？",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ni_hui",
      "speaker_name": "倪慧",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "其实我不该跟你吵架的。我们现在就开始吵架，将来怎么得了？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ni_hui",
      "speaker_name": "倪慧",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "我知道你叫傅红雪，你至少也应该问问我的名字。我叫倪慧，智慧的慧，也就是秀外慧中的慧。我爸爸替我取这名字，只因为我从小就很有智慧。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ni_hui",
      "speaker_name": "倪慧",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "你不信？我不但知道你是干什么来的，而且还能猜出你等的是什么人。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ni_hui",
      "speaker_name": "倪慧",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "你一定是到这地方等着跟别人拼命的，我一看你神色就看得出。你有杀气！",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ni_hui",
      "speaker_name": "倪慧",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "我也知道你等的人一定是杜雷。因为附近几百里地之内，惟一够资格跟傅红雪斗一斗的人，就是杜雷。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_ni_hui",
      "text": "你既然知道，就应该快走！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ni_hui",
      "speaker_name": "倪慧",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "你是不是已经开始在关心我？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_ni_hui",
      "text": "我要你走，只不过因为我杀人并不是给人看的！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ni_hui",
      "speaker_name": "倪慧",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "你就算要我走，也不必太急，杜雷反正不会这么早来的。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ni_hui",
      "speaker_name": "倪慧",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "他一定会让你等，等得心烦意乱时再来。你的心越烦躁，他的机会就越多。这也是种战略。像你这样的人，本来早就应该想到的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ni_hui",
      "speaker_name": "倪慧",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "他要你等，你也可以要他等。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ni_hui",
      "speaker_name": "倪慧",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "我们可以逛一圈再来，我们甚至可以去下两盘棋，喝两杯酒，让他在这里等你，等得他急死为止。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ni_hui",
      "speaker_name": "倪慧",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "我先带你到我们家藏酒的地窖去，如果我们运气好，说不定还可以找到一两坛我姑姑出嫁时留下的女儿红。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ni_hui",
      "speaker_name": "倪慧",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "我只不过想跟你交个朋友，想替你做点事而已，你何必这么样对付我？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_ni_hui",
      "text": "起来，草里有蛇。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ni_hui",
      "speaker_name": "倪慧",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "我全身骨头都快摔散了，你叫我怎么站得起来。我倒不如索性被毒蛇咬死算了。",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ni_hui",
      "speaker_name": "倪慧",
      "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "text": "我现在才知道你以前那个女人为什么要甩下你了，因为你根本不是男人，你不但腿上有毛病，心里也有毛病。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
      "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
      "listener": "char_ni_hui",
      "text": "你走吧。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "拇指",
      "listener": "char_kong_que",
      "text": "他还在等。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kong_que",
      "speaker_name": "孔雀",
      "listener": "char_mu_zhi",
      "text": "我跟他分手的时候，正是未时。他准备再让傅红雪等多久？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "拇指",
      "listener": "char_kong_que",
      "text": "我已经告诉了他，至少要等到申时才去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kong_que",
      "speaker_name": "孔雀",
      "listener": "char_mu_zhi",
      "text": "站在那鬼地方等两个时辰，那种罪只怕很不好受。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "拇指",
      "listener": "char_kong_que",
      "text": "我只担心一件事。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kong_que",
      "speaker_name": "孔雀",
      "listener": "char_mu_zhi",
      "text": "什么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "拇指",
      "listener": "char_kong_que",
      "text": "傅红雪虽然在等，杜雷自己也在等，我只担心他比傅红雪更受不了。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kong_que",
      "speaker_name": "孔雀",
      "listener": "char_mu_zhi",
      "text": "如果他死在傅红雪刀下，你有没有损失？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "拇指",
      "listener": "char_kong_que",
      "text": "没有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kong_que",
      "speaker_name": "孔雀",
      "listener": "char_mu_zhi",
      "text": "那么你有什么好担心的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "拇指",
      "listener": "char_kong_que",
      "text": "我还有个好消息告诉你。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "拇指",
      "listener": "char_kong_que",
      "text": "燕南飞真的已中了毒，而且中的毒很不轻。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kong_que",
      "speaker_name": "孔雀",
      "listener": "char_mu_zhi",
      "text": "这消息是从哪里来的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "拇指",
      "listener": "char_kong_que",
      "text": "是用五百两银子买来的！",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kong_que",
      "speaker_name": "孔雀",
      "listener": "char_mu_zhi",
      "text": "能够值五百两银子的消息，通常都很可靠了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "拇指",
      "listener": "char_kong_que",
      "text": "所以我们随时都可以去杀他了。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kong_que",
      "speaker_name": "孔雀",
      "listener": "char_mu_zhi",
      "text": "我们现在就去。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 6
    }
  ],
